{"tid":1867803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我全家苦口婆心想同班復工醫護講","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T14:39:58.000Z","uid":57911,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfac736aa1b731f156b747dabc56210c054b255","tid":1867803,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"屋企有人做院舍<br />\n院舍缺口罩又買唔到口罩<br />\n用到冇罩都集體打算辭工<br />\n<br />\n想講你哋前線缺物資<br />\n罷工都冇人拍心口保證會有充分物資供應<br />\n你哋係搵自己條命嚟搏<br />\n封關係首要爭取嘅嘢<br />\n但最後有冇封關都要顧自己條命<br />\n冇防禦服冇口罩你應該繼續罷落去<br />\n俾啲高層落嚟做<br />\n高層都有醫護資格<br />\n唔係得你哋有醫護資格<br />\n高層係人命，你哋都係人命<br />\n<br />\n講真過半贊成復工全家都嬲<br />\n嬲你哋唔錫身，嬲你哋唔為自己嘅生命負責"},{"pid":"dfedd46c9d83f46cf72237ce965b66b55afd8291","tid":1867803,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727075bde5f5ad09b6abc74d77d09dbe3e5ac203","tid":1867803,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f7c5808b82e2acebf6d73597188732fc658997","tid":1867803,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117f4a382e97e4a689c191de1d1d9f78ac8b059d","tid":1867803,"uid":39268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工真係好重要<br />\n即使你哋喺公會投票唔贊成罷工都好多可以自己繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使跟公會呢個大台"},{"pid":"59c6936e293e208c73b52737fbe2b4123810aa62","tid":1867803,"uid":206370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}